com.khalsa_ji.ems.builder

Class DesignationBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.khalsa_ji.ems.builder.DesignationBuilder

  • public class DesignationBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    The class DesignationBuilder is a Builder class for the Designation class. It helps in instantiating instances of Designation class by providing a set of methods based on the Builder Design Pattern.
